      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Honey and mustard chicken is a family weeknight dinner that children eat without complaint and adults find deeply satisfying. The slow cooker version is faster to prepare than the oven version. Serve with rice, mashed potato, or new potatoes and a green vegetable.",
